So many cute moments with the kids these past two months. Seeing their little personalities shine makes my heart melt. I truly love being their Mommy. I just wish I could slow these moments down. Time is flying🥹I never want this time with them to end.

Brought back my traditional tree this year! This always brings me back to my childhood. I love involving the kids, and creating these memories with them. @jeannaloveschristmas calls this a Treasure Tree and it really is! So many memories live on this tree! Thank you Jeanna for bringing so much Christmas cheer into our home! It's honestly my favorite tree yet! The beautiful garland she created around the staircase tied everything in so nicely😍Loved it! Nothing like Christmasing with @jeannaloveschristmas Details on everything we used!
